race.description: Mcqueens Tavern (N/P) Tg 1-4W Series 3 F Pr2
race.comment: ELEGANT ZEPHYR (2) used the rails draw to advantage to get home last time at this track and distance (20.04) after leading through, scoring by 1.5 lengths. The one to beat again. LADY TURBINE (8) stalked the pace then proved too strong in the run home to record her maiden win (20.54) at this track over 342m. Boxed wide here. Rates a leading chance again. ADHANA PHILLIP (1) has been out of the placings at his last couple but on the winners' heels when placing three back (20.37) in a TG1-4W at this track. Expected to bounce back to best. COMEBACK ASH (5) can sneak into the finish.
